---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import chevronUp from '../../../public/images/chevronUp.png';
import chevronDown from '../../../public/images/chevronDown.png';
---

<section id="questions" class="px-4 lg:max-w-2xl lg:m-auto">
  <h2 class="sub-title-text mb-10">Common Questions</h2>
  <div>
    <ul class="text-start">
      <li>
        <h3 class="accordeonTitle">What is Wizardshot?
          <span><Image src={chevronUp} alt='checvron up' /></span>
        </h3>
        <p class="accordeonText">Wizardshot is a web app & chrome extension. 
          that allows you to create step-by-step tutorials 
          simply by capturing your screen.
        </p>
        <hr class="mb-10"/>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="accordeonTitle">Whow is Wizardshot Free?
          <span><Image src={chevronUp} alt='checvron up' /></span>
        </h3>
        <p class="accordeonText">The costs to run a service is really inexpensive as most of the processing happens in the Chrome extension.
          Really - all that we have to pay for is <span class="underline">super-secure hosting, awesome 24/7 support</span> and thatâ€™s it. 
          <span>We built Wizardshot as a stand-alone product with a deep <span>Helpjuice Knowledge Base</span> integration.</span> 
        </p>
        <hr class="mb-10"/>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="accordeonTitle">Is my data secure?
          <span><Image src={chevronDown} alt=' checvron down' /></span>
